            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Teudebertus">Teutperto</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Sunibertus">Suniperti</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Teudebertus"
                                >Teudiperto</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Mangnualdus">Magnualdi</name></persName>, habitatores in loco
                            <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Casalini/fundamenta #Landed_possessions #Granaries #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Fruits/vegetables #Chestnuts #Acorns #Hay/fodder"
                            ref="#places/431">Capannule</placeName>, <foreign>donano</foreign> una
                        cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">omnibus rebus</rs> nostris Deo et tibi <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">ecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/68">beati Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, ubi est domo episcoporum, in <rs key="#Cities"
                            >civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Mother_churches" ref="#places/4"
                            >Lucense</placeName>, in primis <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casa habitationis</rs> nostrae cum <rs key="#Casalini/fundamenta"
                            >fundamento</rs>, curte, <rs key="#Granaries">granario</rs>, vel alia
                        edificia ibidem pertenentem, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pratis, paschuis</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">olivetis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Chestnuts">castanetis</rs>, <rs key="#Acorns">silvis,
                            vergariis</rs> (…); tali enim tenore, ut per singulos annos tam nos seu
                        heredes nostros soledum unum ad ipsam Dei ecclesiam reddere debeamus. Et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">res illa</rs> quem habemus in <placeName
                            key="#Placitum/iudicatum #Landed_possessions" ref="#places/580"
                            >Rasiniano</placeName>, <rs key="#Placitum/iudicatum">si ea vincere
                            potuerimus</rs>, medietatem sit in potestate nostra, et medietatem in
                        ipsa Dei ecclesia. <foreign>Se morranno senza eredi, anche il resto sia in
                            potestà di S. Martino</foreign> vel de <rs key="#Priests">sacerdote</rs>
                        qui ibidem ordinatus fuerit. (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Luca</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Teudiperti <rs
                            key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs>; + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Mangnualdus">Magnualdi</name></persName> pater
                        ipsius Teudiperti consentientis; + <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name
                                ref="Arnulus">Arnuli</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs>; + <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Alpari">Alpari</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Cliffo">Clefoni</name></persName>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Pertipertus"
                            >Pertipert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Other_clerics"><name ref="Ostribertus"
                            >Ostripertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
